Installation instructions for apache2 (recommended)
===================================================

* install package ($ sudo apt-get install vpn-user-portal)
* install webserver with php ($ sudo apt install apache2 libapache2-mod-php)
* enable apache config ($ sudo a2enconf vpn-user-portal)
* enable modules ($ sudo a2enmod rewrite headers)
* reload apache ($ sudo systemctl reload apache2)
* initialise ($ sudo -u www-data /usr/bin/vpn-user-portal-init)
